title: Microsoft Excel 2003 - Portable Version
description:
Microsoft Excel 2003 - Portable Version



Description:

	 
	This version of Microsoft Excel 2003 was made especially for USB flash drives as it does not require any installation. Put this on your USB flash drive or portable hard disk and use it on just about any Windows computer (Internet cafe, school, library etc. ).

	Everything you would normally find on an "installed" version of Excel 2003 is included in this portable version.



Note:

	For those who are new to portable applications, this can also be used from a local hard drive on most Windows PCs.



Instructions:


	1. Unpack the .7z file using WinRAR (or 7zip).

	2. You should get a folder called "Excel 2003 Portable".

	3. If you plan on using this on a USB storage device, place the "Excel 2003 Portable" folder on your USB device. 

	4. Inside the "Excel 2003 Portable" folder, double click on the "Microsoft Office Excel 2003.exe" file to start using the application.
